7ca1931","tid":1663381,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91f5eb10c195a8c5e4d0f7c21ec5768bc36a438","tid":1663381,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"睇樣都知支那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c577a2f5fc68d3b6cedff45ee24617a1ee924a","tid":1663381,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"44e970285ec281da013939dcca2e0aa5501daa8b","tid":1663381,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:34:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49fb01bea50ac515ed0a76e7812ade3e3e62b778","tid":1663381,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f169eab7f9dc02f2a38f1cea0fd9d9a0b0ce3b7a","tid":1663381,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43e1d01f954db13060440d6549dcaaed222e376a","tid":1663381,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"694fe35b2d48a10ed044f664d8e2edf6b1ed4540","tid":1663381,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"A. <br />\n13 分鐘前<br />\n識人做Popo<br />\n兇手去咗大埔狗屋自殺<br />\n黑警唔想做condom就告鳩